Achievements.Name: Winning Streak
Achievements.Description: Win 3 race events back to back in either Arcade or Single Player Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: 1-2 Finish
Achievements.Description: Complete a Ranked Match Team Championship with your team taking the top two positions.

Achievements.Name: Team Domination
Achievements.Description: Complete a Ranked Match Team Championship with your team taking up the top four positions.

Achievements.Name: Team Leader
Achievements.Description: Earn the most points for your team in a Ranked Match Team Championship.

Achievements.Name: Showboater
Achievements.Description: Earn 9000 Kudos in a single race.

Achievements.Name: 5-Star Racer
Achievements.Description: Earn 5 Kudos Stars.

Achievements.Name: Superstar
Achievements.Description: Earn 5 Kudos Stars three times in a race.

Achievements.Name: Mind Your Manners
Achievements.Description: Win a Street Race in Arcade or Gotham Career mode without making contact with walls.

Achievements.Name: The Unicyclist
Achievements.Description: Perform a long Wheelie on a motorcycle.

Achievements.Name: Bibendum
Achievements.Description: Play all 3 Test Track disciplines and set a score in each one.

Achievements.Name: Weather Master
Achievements.Description: Win races in rain, fog, and snow in either Arcade or Single Player Career modes.

Achievements.Name: Winner
Achievements.Description: Win your first event in either Arcade or Single Player Career modes.

Achievements.Name: Silver Gotham Arcader
Achievements.Description: Earn a Silver medal in every Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Gold Gotham Arcader
Achievements.Description: Earn a Gold medal in every Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Platinum Gotham Arcader
Achievements.Description: Earn a Platinum medal in every Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Silver Double
Achievements.Description: Earn at least a Silver medal with both a bike and a car in any Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Gold Double
Achievements.Description: Earn at least a Gold medal with both a bike and a car in any Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Platinum Double
Achievements.Description: Earn at least a Platinum medal with both a bike and a car in any Arcade event.

Achievements.Name: Arcade Chapter Complete
Achievements.Description: Complete any chapter in Arcade mode.

Achievements.Name: Professional
Achievements.Description: Reach the rank of Professional in Single Player Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Hotshot
Achievements.Description: Reach the rank of Hotshot in Single Player Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Master
Achievements.Description: Reach the rank of Master in Single Player Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Hero
Achievements.Description: Become a National Champion in Single Player Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Champion
Achievements.Description: Win your first Championship in either Single Player Career or Ranked Match play.

Achievements.Name: Motorcycle Ace
Achievements.Description: Win a Single Player Career Championship on a motorcycle.

Achievements.Name: Major Winner
Achievements.Description: Win a Major in Single Player Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Dominator
Achievements.Description: Win all three Single Player Career Majors.

Achievements.Name: Stuntman
Achievements.Description: Perform your first stunt on a bike.

Achievements.Name: Buy an Achievement
Achievements.Description: Buy the K1,000,000 gamer picture to earn this Achievement.

Achievements.Name: Back it Up!
Achievements.Description: In a split-screen Street Race, finish 1st and 2nd in reverse gear against at least one AI opponent.

Achievements.Name: Strike a Pose
Achievements.Description: Get two bikes facing each other, 15 metres apart, with each performing an impressive endo.

Achievements.Name: First Timer
Achievements.Description: Complete your first Ranked Match Championship.

Achievements.Name: 8th Wonder of the World
Achievements.Description: Complete a lap of the Michelin Test Track 'figure of 8' while sliding.

Achievements.Name: Catch 'Em All
Achievements.Description: Swap paint with every opponent in an eight vehicle race.

Achievements.Name: Endo King
Achievements.Description: Earn 100 Kudos by performing an Endo with a motorcycle.

Achievements.Name: Seat of your Pants
Achievements.Description: Complete a Hot Lap event in Arcade mode without touching your brake.

Achievements.Name: Rubbin' is Racin'
Achievements.Description: Knock off the wing mirrors on all of your opponents' vehicles in a Single Player Street Race event.

Achievements.Name: Show Jump
Achievements.Description: Get eight vehicles in the air at the same time.

Achievements.Name: I Love PGR
Achievements.Description: Buy everything in the PGR Shop or complete PGR 3 and get to Rank #1

Achievements.Name: Whitewash
Achievements.Description: Win every event in a Single Player or Ranked Match Championship.

Achievements.Name: You Won't Believe Your Eyes!
Achievements.Description: Create a 3D image using Photo Mode.

Achievements.Name: Secret Agent
Achievements.Description: Puzzle #2

Achievements.Name: 3CZV657
Achievements.Description: Puzzle #1

Achievements.Name: Tonight Make Me Unstoppable
Achievements.Description: Puzzle #3

Achievements.Name: Play It Again Sam
Achievements.Description: Improve on a medal earned in any arcade event

Achievements.Name: PGR On Demand - Photo
Achievements.Description: Upload a photo and vote on a photo in PGR On Demand

Achievements.Name: PGR On Demand - Video
Achievements.Description: Upload a replay and vote on a replay using PGR On Demand

Achievements.Name: Giant Killer
Achievements.Description: Win against a human opponent with Rank 1 single player status on Xbox LIVE.

Achievements.Name: Numero Uno
Achievements.Description: Reach Rank Number One on the Single Player Career Drivers' Leaderboard.

Achievements.Name: Beat Bizarre
Achievements.Description: Defeat a PGR 4 team member on Xbox LIVE, or defeat anyone who's bested a PGR 4 team member.
